			Company Description 


			DGSE Cos., Inc. engages in the jewelry business. Its activities include buying and selling all kinds of jewelries including diamonds, fine watches, rare coins and currency, precious metal bullion products, scrap gold, silver, platinum, and palladium as well as collectibles and other valuables. It of...
		


                DGSE Cos., Inc. engages in the jewelry business. Its activities include buying and selling all kinds of jewelries including diamonds, fine watches, rare coins and currency, precious metal bullion products, scrap gold, silver, platinum, and palladium as well as collectibles and other valuables. It offers its products through retail and wholesale store. The company was founded on September 16, 1965 and is headquartered in Dallas, TX.
            




