Welcome to Dallas Gold & Silver Exchange, Inc.
Dallas Gold & Silver Exchange, Inc. is your number one location in Dallas, TX to buy and sell bracelets and earrings, and to purchase used wedding jewelry, used Rolex watches, and watch accessories. In addition to being able to buy and sell wedding jewelry, you can also buy and sell gold coins, silver coins, and currency. Our integrity and outstanding customer service has made us the name you can trust for all of your jewelry and coin buying and selling needs.
Safely Purchase and Sell High End, Quality Jewelry
Whether you are interested in beautiful used diamond rings, pre-owned rolex watches, or any other type of jewelry, you can trust that Dallas Gold & Silver Exchange, Inc. will provide you with the right solutions. Here you can safely buy and sell women’s bands, semi mounts, men bands, and eternity bands. We make the selling and acquisition of fine jewelry in Dallas, TX a simple and straightforward process. We take care of wholesale, retail and institutional clientele with an unsurpassed level of service.
When you want to buy and sell collectibles, copper nickel coins, rare coins, buillons, watches, diamonds or jewelry of any kind, you can trust that DGSE will provide the best services. We also provide jewelry and watch repair services right onsite.
Contact Us
Contact us for more information about how to buy and sell necklaces, eternity bands, bridal sets, and all types of rings such as anniversary rings or engagement rings. Fill out our contact form for any inquiries regarding our services or products for sale.
 









