Fine Estate Jewelry, Pre-Owned Engagement Rings, Diamond Earrings, Gently-Used Rolex & More
DGSE – A Premier Estate Jeweler Since 1965
Dallas Gold & Silver Exchange is a long-established, publicly traded jewelry dealer offering a designer estate jewelry collection hand-picked by buyers who are as selective as our customers.
Visit us online at DGSE.com or stop by at any of our stores in Arlington, Dallas, Euless, and Southlake for estate jewelry including pre-owned wedding jewelry, diamond earrings, wedding bands, bracelets, gently used Rolex watches and more.
Fine Pre-Owned Estate Jewelry
Estate jewelry holds a treasure trove of finely crafted designer pieces to explore – exquisite pre-owned diamond earrings, wedding rings and bands unlike those you see at a typical jeweler. View our collection of designer jewelry, pre-owned diamond necklaces and wedding rings online. Whether you're looking for yellow gold, white gold, or platinum, with princess cut or round brilliant cut diamonds, we invite you to explore our jewelry and rings in every cut and design.
Used Rolex for Men & Women
DGSE is known for its repertoire of pre-owned Rolex watches. View our used Rolex watches to find vintage or gently used modern models like the sought-after pre-owned Rolex Datejust for men and ladies and Submariner, curated from estate sales. Find certified pre-owned Rolexes and other fine estate watches for sale online and in our boutique stores.
Trusted Online Jewelry Store for Estate Jewelry & Pre-Owned Diamond Rings















